---

<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:py-20 text-center fade-in-section">
  <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl text-brown-dark mb-8 sm:mb-10">Plan del fin de semana</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 sm:space-y-8 text-left max-w-lg mx-auto">
    <!-- Viernes -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:gap-4 sm:items-start pl-3 sm:pl-0 border-l-2 border-gold-lighter sm:border-l-0"
    >
      <div class="flex sm:flex-col sm:flex-shrink-0 sm:w-20 sm:text-right gap-2 sm:gap-0">
        <p class="font-heading text-gold text-base sm:text-lg">Viernes</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-warm">15 mayo</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden sm:block flex-shrink-0 w-px bg-gold-lighter self-stretch min-h-[2.5rem]"></div>
      <div class="min-w-0">
        <p class="font-semibold text-brown-dark text-sm sm:text-base">Llegada y bienvenida</p>
        <p class="text-gray-warm text-sm mt-0.5">Cena informal para los que lleguéis el viernes. Os avisaremos del sitio.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sábado -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:gap-4 sm:items-start pl-3 sm:pl-0 border-l-2 border-gold-lighter sm:border-l-0"
    >
      <div class="flex sm:flex-col sm:flex-shrink-0 sm:w-20 sm:text-right gap-2 sm:gap-0">
        <p class="font-heading text-gold text-base sm:text-lg">Sábado</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-warm">16 mayo</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden sm:block flex-shrink-0 w-px bg-gold-lighter self-stretch min-h-[2.5rem]"></div>
      <div class="min-w-0">
        <p class="font-semibold text-brown-dark text-sm sm:text-base">El gran día</p>
        <p class="text-gray-warm text-sm mt-0.5">
          11:00 Ceremonia &middot; 14:30 Comida (Espacio Emboca) &middot; Fiesta hasta que el cuerpo aguante
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Domingo -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:gap-4 sm:items-start pl-3 sm:pl-0 border-l-2 border-gold-lighter sm:border-l-0"
    >
      <div class="flex sm:flex-col sm:flex-shrink-0 sm:w-20 sm:text-right gap-2 sm:gap-0">
        <p class="font-heading text-gold text-base sm:text-lg">Domingo</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-warm">17 mayo</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden sm:block flex-shrink-0 w-px bg-gold-lighter self-stretch min-h-[2.5rem]"></div>
      <div class="min-w-0">
        <p class="font-semibold text-brown-dark text-sm sm:text-base">Despedida</p>
        <p class="text-gray-warm text-sm mt-0.5">
          Desayuno tranquilo y tiempo libre para disfrutar de la ciudad antes de volver.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
